MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 1603

CREATING AND DESIGNATING SEVERAL PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PRIVATE DOMAIN SITUATED AT BARANGAY BIÑANG, MUNICIPALITY OF BIÑAN, PROVINCE OF LAGUNA AS SPECIAL ECONOMIC ZONE PURSUANT TO REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7916 AS AMENDED BY REPUBLIC ACT NO. 8748

Pursuant to the powers vested in me under Republic Act No. 7916, otherwise known as the Special Economic Zone Act of 1995 as amended by Republic Act No. 8748 and upon recommendation of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Philippines, do hereby create and designate several parcels of land, subject to the provisions of Republic Act No. 7916 as amended, its Implementing Rules and Regulations and Resolution No. 07-436 dated 24 September 2007, of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, located at Barangay Biñang, Biñan, Laguna as special economic zone , to be known as Laguna Technopark Annex with an aggregate area of Two Hundred Ninety Thousand One Hundred Fifty Five (290,155) Square Meters , more or less, as defined by the following technical description:

